drh added on 2014-04-20 09:34:23:
In the query at the end of the following code, the ORDER BY clause is ignored
and the results appear in the wrong order:
CREATE TABLE t1(x,y);
INSERT INTO t1 VALUES(1,1),(2,0);
CREATE INDEX t1yx ON t1(y,x);
SELECT x,y FROM t1 GROUP BY x, y ORDER BY x, y;
This problem appears to have been introduced into trunk by the cutover to the
next generation query planner in check-in [0fe31f60cadc5fe5a9d]
on 2013-06-26.
